e-date=25 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Guangxi,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910597.html|title=\u5e7f\u897f\u542f\u52a8\u91cd\u5927\u7a81\u53d1\u516c\u5171\u536b\u751f\u4e8b\u4ef6\u4e00\u7ea7\u54cd\u5e94{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=24 January 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125072917/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910597.html|archive-date=25 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> and Hebei<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910664.html|title=\u6cb3\u5317\u7701\u542f\u52a8\u91cd\u5927\u7a81\u53d1\u516c\u5171\u536b\u751f\u4e8b\u4ef6\u4e00\u7ea7\u54cd\u5e94{{!}}\u754c\u9762\u65b0\u95fb \u00b7 \u5feb\u8baf|website=www.jiemian.com|access-date=25 January 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125160947/https://www.jiemian.com/article/3910664.html|archive-date=25 January 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> declared a level 1 public health emergency, in chronological order.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cgtn.com/special/Battling-the-novel-coronavirus-What-we-know-so-far-.html|title=Latest on the coronavirus outbreak: 881 cases confirmed, 26 dead|last=|first=|date=January 23, 2020|website=CGTN|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129051251/https://www.cgtn.com/special/Battling-the-novel-coronavirus-What-we-know-so-far-.html|archive-date=January 29, 2020|access-date=}}</ref> The city of [[Jingzhou]] was quarantined, raising the number of people in quarantined cities to 35 million.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mobile.twitter.com/BNONews/status/1220578836259229697|title=BREAKING: Chinese city of Jingzhou to be put on lockdown at 5 p.m., raising number of people in locked down cities to 35 million|last=|first=|date=January 24, 2020|website=BNO News|access-date=}}</ref> The entire Hubei province now came under a city-by-city quarantine, save for [[Xiangyang]] and [[Shennongjia|Shennongjia Forestry District]].\n\nAll 70,000 Chinese c